wtftools (0.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial public release.
  * 19 subcommands + wtfd daemon, 38 built-in checks, plugin SDK
    (bash + Python).
  * wtfd HTTP daemon with /audit, /audit.json, /audit.prom, /history,
    /snapshot/N, POST /run-now endpoints. Bundled systemd unit.
  * Multi-host fleet aggregation (wtf fleet), host-to-host drift detection
    (wtf compare), both with --watch and --run-now.
  * LLM bridge: wtf explain --llm ollama|claude|openai|auto.
  * Output formats: text, json, csv, plain, html, prometheus.
  * Docker image, GitHub Actions release workflow.

 -- Aleksandr Pimenov <wachawo@gmail.com>  Wed, 20 May 2026 12:00:00 +0000
